Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來買鰤魚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.27,0:01:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天有好貨喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.40,0:01:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要做鰤魚煮蘿蔔嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.94,0:01:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 因為天氣一直很冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.73,0:01:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼甜的香味是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.36,0:01:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁傳過來的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.82,0:01:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為明天就是情人節了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.73,0:01:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情人節？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.99,0:02:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(116,203)\fs18\fnsimhei\bord0\shad1\1c&Hffffff&\fade(255,0,255,0,1500,5800,6800)}第9話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.99,0:02:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(174,233)\fs24\fnsimhei\bord0\shad1\1c&Hffffff&\fade(255,0,255,0,1500,5800,6800)}比愛還甜蜜   卻有點苦澀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著只要讓巧克力醬冷卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.89,0:02:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和 成型的時候要小心一點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.87,0:02:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道怎樣呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.13,0:02:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿不下來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.57,0:02:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.90,0:02:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『冷靜一點…』\N不對…好像冷了就會硬掉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.03,0:02:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.08,0:02:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.51,0:02:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個有著苦澀少女心味道的杏仁巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.41,0:02:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著只要把這個送給喜歡的人就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.87,0:02:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.24,0:02:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.78,0:02:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.12,0:02:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.76,0:02:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 我不是那種意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.82,0:02:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天叫做情人節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.43,0:02:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是女孩子會送巧克力給喜歡的男孩子的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.69,0:03:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要送給男孩子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我送給阿優…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和 …
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.82,0:03:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那個意思啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.25,0:03:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…也就是說啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.34,0:03:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說明才好呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.88,0:03:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.88,0:03:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.14,0:03:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是戀愛的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是姐姐把巧克力送給自己深愛的阿優一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.73,0:03:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也把巧克力送給我愛著的人就行了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.39,0:03:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你你你你在說些什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.05,0:03:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是隨處可見極為平常的女傭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能對主人做這種大膽無恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.97,0:03:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天理不容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背棄社會道德良知的事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.12,0:03:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的不會的不會的～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.84,0:03:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那樣的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.15,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…而且話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的心到底又是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和 你放心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為也有種社會系統叫做義理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送給濱口怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濱口他一定會很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濱口…同學？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.39,0:04:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那姐姐你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 這個小包是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪里開始聽的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大膽無恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天理不容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背棄社會道德良知…這附近開始的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣相當冷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經幫你放了熱水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.67,0:04:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐是吃鰤魚煮蘿蔔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燒焦了燒焦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快澆點水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.78,0:04:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～是油啊～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.76,0:04:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,370 我想今天應該是最後一次跟你見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.25,0:05:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下個禮拜我預定好的時間表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天全部都被取消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.82,0:05:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.04,0:05:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都像這樣消失了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.65,0:05:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,369…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,370 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.49,0:05:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要趕快逃走才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.47,0:05:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做連你也會被抹消喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,370 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.03,0:05:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有一次也好 我想試試心跳加速的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.41,0:05:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想因為高興而笑著看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要有心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.96,0:05:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要繼續活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.79,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天可以得到心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我約定好 你的這裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天一定會有心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約定好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了 下雪了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊還沒有人踏過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪耶～都還沒有人踏過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.67,0:06:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕千鶴 總是一直無憂無慮的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.77,0:06:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我先說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.06,0:06:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想一個人偷跑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.89,0:06:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年我可是很認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.73,0:06:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們兩個想的事都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這樣打算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濱口來啦？早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.46,0:07:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人真是心裏想什麼都會寫在臉上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這只是義理的而已喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.67,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和絕對不會送我巧克力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.29,0:07:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.18,0:07:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這根本不會發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.90,0:07:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可奈何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.37,0:07:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.36,0:07:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安藤她跌到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天誰負責急救啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和 你還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.58,0:07:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道美奈和她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濱口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對…這種事根本不會發生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那個巧克力是要送給誰的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是二班的田中？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 一班的後藤也對美奈和…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.66,0:08:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是八田學長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說是老師？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和 到底是誰啊～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濱口 冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.55,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 還不知道是誰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定知道的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是要送給誰的啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.07,0:08:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽她說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少騙人了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我不問了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全沒精神了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好消沉喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2月14日到底是要幹嘛啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是建國紀念日的三天後而已嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…現在換成自暴自棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.50,0:08:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光看都覺得他很可憐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在不能就這樣放著他不管吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這詭異的氣氛到底是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…是追著我而來的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.89,0:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.37,0:09:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.43,0:09:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…1年5班33號的田中佳美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.05,0:09:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.85,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是很不巧我現在沒辦法動…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.95,0:09:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能請你先放這裏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.18,0:09:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都給我這個然後跑走…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.22,0:09:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道這是種新式的娛樂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.62,0:09:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩子愛著老師啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是愛的發球喔 給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送過來又送過去的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.01,0:10:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都中了巧克力公司的計了啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濱口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.42,0:10:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點東西要給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.68,0:10:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川原 難道你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經忍不住了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.07,0:10:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川原…你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是安藤拜託我拿來給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說的這麼曖昧啦 我差點就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鹿亂撞嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.00,0:10:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是安藤…也就是美奈和…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有東西想要給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.89,0:10:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在有著夕陽餘輝的山丘上等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.48,0:10:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安藤美奈和上…(心)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濱口冷靜點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.02,0:10:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 你拿得太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.56,0:10:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你傳達得太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.85,0:10:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會被誤會的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.22,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是『有著夕陽餘輝的山丘』…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.13,0:11:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是『有著夕陽餘輝的山丘』我還以為在哪里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.50,0:11:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不要看不起這裏喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏告白的成功率可是100%喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有誰做過啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.57,0:11:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在川原正在叫濱口過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.40,0:11:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概沒事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵啾~好冷…
