Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.90,0:11:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.52,0:11:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情人節巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼好香的醬油味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經很少有女孩子會送義理巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.54,0:11:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年可是真心的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是真心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟往常是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優陷入危機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下子有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.01,0:12:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是想說先從千鶴的巧克力拿起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.91,0:12:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後混水摸魚過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.02,0:12:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,球掉到哪里去了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.14,0:12:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪的日子要看好腳踏車才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.16,0:12:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有手伸出來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿來做雪人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴 手 眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.49,0:13:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.71,0:13:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了…巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.58,0:13:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我的心靈多麼寒冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.52,0:13:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體卻總是火熱的燃燒著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.19,0:13:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師…你什麼時候來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.63,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美裏君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請先吃我的情人節巧克力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.42,0:13:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後我再讓你吃更甜的東西喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…麻煩人物又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.69,0:13:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.62,0:13:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如各位所見 這是由我的胸部忠實重現的巧克力喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還摻了超強力的營養劑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.65,0:13:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子我們的甜蜜夜晚會更加甜蜜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.52,0:13:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎斬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.94,0:13:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛死了 你在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的力作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個造型實在是太難看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.08,0:14:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不是說弄碎了就不能吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這大小的確正好入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.64,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣怎樣？好吃還是難吃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美裏君 你要吃誰的巧克力呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.15,0:14:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是想逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.38,0:14:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在阿優你吃之前我們會一直在這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧 快吃吧 快吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.90,0:14:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.16,0:14:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.12,0:14:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.74,0:15:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川原那傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的在這裏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 茶梗立起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用那個來代替吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.35,0:15:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-請買巧克力吧-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.79,0:15:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我一個小時的話我就給你巧克力當謝禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.27,0:15:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店就拜託你一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.38,0:16:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪的日子 小心不要滑倒 注意喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.58,0:16:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 巧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.34,0:16:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雪的日子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力…巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.78,0:16:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把巧克力還我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.19,0:16:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 有魔法師耶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小真 哪會有那種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.82,0:16:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 因為那是我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧…巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.11,0:17:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.28,0:17:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌好像生氣了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.66,0:17:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來不像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我稍微有反省一下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.43,0:17:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿優面對這種事情\N為什麼老是這麼遲鈍呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.82,0:17:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.55,0:17:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得他好像每年都很巧妙的帶過去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.41,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.44,0:17:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優是那種把友情看的比戀愛還重要的那種人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.41,0:17:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像我們一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.71,0:17:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然今天是這麼特別的日子\N我們就多散步一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴為什麼會這麼有精神呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.53,0:17:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為那個超強力營養劑嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.47,0:17:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,式條老師的那個嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她果然加了那種東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.93,0:18:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒有辦法的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法…算了吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個樣子是發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.35,0:18:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說不送巧克力不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只買得起這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你真的很辛苦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.35,0:18:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…阿優…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.85,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力…你認為怎樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.35,0:18:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又回想起來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天可真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.01,0:19:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在已經覺得一輩子都吃不下巧克力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.53,0:19:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.24,0:19:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一輩子都吃不下之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.14,0:19:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想…再吃一個也不錯啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.16,0:19:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 你可以不用勉強自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.77,0:19:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是叫你馬上就要吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.45,0:19:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請收下來慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便這個也給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仙貝耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.41,0:19:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你吃完甜食後會想吃點鹹的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.46,0:19:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你泡茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐深愛著阿優…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.51,0:19:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深愛著……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.87,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 你臉怎麼紅紅的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.11,0:20:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你想太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是茶喝太多的關係！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙好燙好燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是又感冒了？
